# ==============================================================================
# Sovereign Administrative Gateway Environment Configuration Example
# ==============================================================================
# Copy this file to '.env' and populate with your production credentials.
# Any sensitive keys should NEVER be committed to version control.

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 🤖 1. Google Gemini AI Service Setup
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Required for AI-powered assistant features, customer support copilots,
# translation features, and smart feedback summarization.
# Obtain your key from the Google AI Studio console: https://aistudio.google.com/
GEMINI_API_KEY="your_google_gemini_api_key_here"

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 🌐 2. Application Live Deployment URL
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# The fully qualified domain name (FQDN) where this application is hosted.
# Used for generating dynamic sitemap.xml files, validating QR codes, 
# self-referential links, and OAuth redirect callback URLs.
APP_URL="https://mas-sovereign-tours.com"

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 🔒 3. Administrative Passcode Clearance Tiers
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Next-generation security passcodes for staff and administrative dashboards.
# Verified securely server-side to prevent client-bundle leakages.
# These values should be 4-digit strings for optimum tactical keypad usability.

# Level 3: Sovereign Admin (Default demo: 8899)
# Master administrative privilege over CMS, CRM dossiers, and audit trails.
ADMIN_PIN="8899"

# Level 2: Operations Manager (Default demo: 4455)
# Logistics scheduling for expert Egyptologists, Benz chauffeurs, and coupons.
OPERATIONS_PIN="4455"

# Level 1: Guest Relations Coordinator (Default demo: 2233)
# Guest database communications, bulk WhatsApp campaign dispatch, support tickets.
CRM_PIN="2233"

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 💾 4. Disaster Recovery Encryption Configurations
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Secret key used to encrypt daily database backups via AES-256 before storage
# to prevent unauthorized reads in case of direct bucket access.
BACKUP_ENCRYPTION_KEY="sovereign_mas_disaster_recovery_aes_key"

